THE MEGAWOLOLO TANK was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 05 October 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

THE MEGAWOLOLO TANK is the combination of the four Wololo Tank: Swastika Temple Wololo Tankcopter, Neo Caliph Wololo Tank, Neo Templar Wololo Tank, & Lord Gautama Wololo Tank. This titan-like celestial tank is “manufactured” for special holy pilgrimage occasions and is only available in 10 editions across the universe. Mounted with triple Faith Canon, two Rotor Swastika (Offensive & Defensive), one Pink G Gun, and Moonstar Caliph’s Shield. This gentle beast is fully capable of wreak havoc on the battlefields and protects the entire realm with a simple command, yes, this is automatic & self sustain vessels installed with the latest hyper-advanced A.I. & software inside.
Command & conquer the entire galaxies, be the next leader, and create your own chaotic beauty universe.
